{"TopicId":119991,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"[1.1.3] BDArmory FPS - A BDArmory Expansion - 0.4 (9-10-16)","CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-02T19:40:59Z","PageNum":7,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:13:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMac 11 sure does fill the void of a SMG.\u003Cbr\u003E\nNow we don\u0027t have to lug around those bulky 20mm vulcans\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nOnly thing i would suggest is move the gun back a bit more so it looks like the kerbal is holding it by the grip rather than the stock\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Acea","CreatedById":98766,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:20:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402450\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455131603\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMac 11 sure does fill the void of a SMG.\u003Cbr\u003E\nNow we don\u0027t have to lug around those bulky 20mm vulcans\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nOnly thing i would suggest is move the gun back a bit more so it looks like the kerbal is holding it by the grip rather than the stock\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck out NAS there\u0027s a STEN available\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:22:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402461\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455132019\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298766\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Acea\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Acea said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck out NAS there\u0027s a STEN available\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have but unless you have updated it lately it doesnt have a turret factor in it. Its stationary like the BD m2 .50 cal LMG\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso i can\u0027t check to see if you have until my new computer charger comes in as mine has a short in it. But it should be in today\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-10T19:24:29Z\u0022 title=\u002202/10/2016 07:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 10, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by War Eagle 1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Acea","CreatedById":98766,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:30:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402468\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455132133\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have but unless you have updated it lately it doesnt have a turret factor in it. Its stationary like the BD m2 .50 cal LMG\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso i can\u0027t check to see if you have until my new computer charger comes in as mine has a short in it. But it should be in today\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes it works in this way because I want to simulate an invasion action in which you don\u0027t have much time to take aim. A sten is not a very accurate or reliable weapon, and doesn\u0027t work like a turret, but it does do some damage, which should be fine\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:35:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402479\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455132636\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298766\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Acea\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Acea said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes it works in this way because I want to simulate an invasion action in which you don\u0027t have much time to take aim. A sten is not a very accurate or reliable weapon, and doesn\u0027t work like a turret, but it does do some damage, which should be fine\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can see where you are going but for this mod we are trying to get it to function in guard mode. So really i guess its just two different ideas of looking at how to use it.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nInterestingly enough. The Stern in still somewhat in use. When my dad was in Iraq (LT Col. so he didn\u0027t actually fight), he got to fire many of the weapons the terrorist\u00A0use which included the Stern. To quote my dad \u0022It was a fun gun!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Acea","CreatedById":98766,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:39:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402486\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455132906\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can see where you are going but for this mod we are trying to get it to function in guard mode. So really i guess its just two different ideas of looking at how to use it.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nInterestingly enough. The Stern in still somewhat in use. When my dad was in Iraq (LT Col. so he didn\u0027t actually fight), he got to fire many of the weapons the terrorist\u00A0use which included the Stern. To quote my dad \u0022It was a fun gun!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah I agree the weapon is quite interesting and creative to\u00A0the time it was developed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-10T19:39:35Z\u0022 title=\u002202/10/2016 07:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 10, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Acea\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:41:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402497\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455133148\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298766\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Acea\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Acea said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah I agree the weapon is quite interesting and creative for\u00A0the time it was developed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you consider adding it to BD FPS with turret functions?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso Jester...you should consider asking BahamotoD to put a link to this mod on the front of his page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Acea","CreatedById":98766,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:45:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455133284\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you consider adding it to BD FPS with turret functions?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso Jester...you should consider asking BahamotoD to put a link to this mod on the front of his page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot hard I guess and I may consider seeking a way to give\u00A0it a relatively realistic turret performance, which may take some time\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:46:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455133284\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould you consider adding it to BD FPS with turret functions?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso Jester...you should consider asking BahamotoD to put a link to this mod on the front of his page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can request it if you\u0027d like. I was honestly waiting for others to suggest adding it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlooks like I\u0027ll need to post Spanners work in the OP,\u00A0because you two just buried it in about 10 seconds \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T19:53:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data