te=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402578\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455135791\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250907\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpannerMonkey(smce)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, SpannerMonkey(smce) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlamethrower muwahahaha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLol good luck.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nRifles:\u003Cbr\u003E\nM4/M16\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nAK-47/74\u003Cbr\u003E\nTavor 21\u003Cbr\u003E\nSCAR-H\u003Cbr\u003E\nG-36\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSMG:\u003Cbr\u003E\nMP-5\u003Cbr\u003E\nMac-11 (thanks Spanner)\u003Cbr\u003E\nUZI\u003Cbr\u003E\nUMP\u003Cbr\u003E\nP90\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nLMG:\u003Cbr\u003E\nM249\u003Cbr\u003E\nM60\u003Cbr\u003E\nPKP\u003Cbr\u003E\nL86\u003Cbr\u003E\nRPD\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nPistols: (add a reload feature to make it semi auto)\u003Cbr\u003E\nM9\u003Cbr\u003E\nGlock\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nIWI Desert Eagle\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnti Vehicle launchers:\u003Cbr\u003E\n(For the most part the AT-4 has that covered but if possible)\u003Cbr\u003E\nFGM-148\u003Cbr\u003E\nRemodel the 40mm grenade launcher to look more like the\u00A0Milkor MGL\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnti Air Launchers:\u003Cbr\u003E\nFIM-92\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T20:43:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402607\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0