2 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402578\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455135791\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250907\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpannerMonkey(smce)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n44 minutes ago, SpannerMonkey(smce) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlamethrower muwahahaha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust don\u0027t spend all your energy here. I want to see Boomstick resurrected \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-10T21:08:00Z\u0022 title=\u002202/10/2016 09:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 10, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by V8jester\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T20:48:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402617\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455137018\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022136093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V8jester\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, V8jester said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo which part of that list are you working on? Hmmmmm \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks to Kerbal animation suite, I could in theory do a reload animation. But the guns are spawned in such a way that don\u0027t move... So I have no idea how you\u0027d actually do a reload using the systems we are using.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrust me if I had any know how I would be making the guns myself. Really the list I gave is just to get the wheels turning but I\u0027m not expecting all of them\u003Cbr\u003E\nNow I\u0027m not saying have them actually reload but make some like the pistols semi auto (one bullet per trigger pull). Basically like how the 105mm howitzer has a time delay in-between shots you could set up the pistols to do something similar to give it the effect of not pew pew pew but rather pew...pew...pew\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T21:07:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402624\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455137298\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrust me if I had any know how I would be making the guns myself. Really the list I gave is just to get the wheels turning but I\u0027m not expecting all of them\u003Cbr\u003E\nNow I\u0027m not saying have them actually reload but make some like the pistols semi auto (one bullet per trigger pull). Basically like how the 105mm howitzer has a time delay in-between shots you could set up the pistols to do something similar to give it the effect of not pew pew pew but rather pew...pew...pew\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s totally do able. The other thing I can do for people that have the inclination is setup a separate batch of cfg files for \u0022Prop only\u0022 guns. The props will not fire but will act the same as a ProProps parts. This would be for people using Kerbal Animation Suite to be able to have the Kerbal move a gun around in a more realistic fashion for videos which will respond the the bone mesh\u0027s in the Kerbal\u0027s hands. Then when\u00A0you need them to fire, you can swap the prop out for an actual \u0022BD turret\u0022 gun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a thought. If enough people are interested I may release a side download for the diehard cinematic guys. Or just instructions how to convert the cfg\u0027s on your own.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-10T21:11:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222402657\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455138441\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022136093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V8jester\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, V8jester said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s totally do able. The other thing I can do for people that have the inclination is setup a separate batch of cfg files for \u0022Prop only\u0022 guns. The props will not fire but will act the same as a ProProps parts. This would be for people using Kerbal Animation Suite to be able to have the Kerbal move a gun around in a more realistic fashion for videos which will respond the the bone mesh\u0027s in the Kerbal\u0027s hands. Then when\u00A0you need them to fire, you can swap the prop out for an actual \u0022BD turret\u0022 gun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a thought. If enough people are interested I may release a side download for the diehard cinematic guys. Or just instructions how to convert the cfg\u0027s on your own.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf i was able to do kip cinematics i would 100% support that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpannerMonkey(smce)","CreatedById":50907,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T22:44:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDesert Eagle,,,,, check\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nM16 A1 ,,,,,,,check\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill tweaking bits n bobs but i like em \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/KZJW0Mj.png\u0022 alt=\u0022KZJW0Mj.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/DBBuTWD.png\u0022 alt=\u0022DBBuTWD.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T23:54:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222404440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455230654\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022