/kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-12T00:58:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222404543\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455235181\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250907\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpannerMonkey(smce)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, SpannerMonkey(smce) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat worries me the most is the insane grins the kerbs get on their little green faces when firing weapons,\u00A0 glad you like em\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd i did give the deagle a sensible firing pattern, esp as i couldn\u0027t resist making the the AE model, hand held cannon indeed \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs a gun enthusiast myself i find the grins normal lol.\u003Cbr\u003E\nI can\u0027t wait to test them myself.\u003Cbr\u003E\nOne thing you should consider doing (if possible) is make it so that rounds fired from those guns like that M16 or Mac-11 have as little affect on things like armor as possible but still able to make a kerbal pop with enough rounds. \u00A0That way it can\u0027t kill tanks (easily) but is still combat effective.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-12T17:29:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust realized, I never said:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the team Spanner!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-12T17:42:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow! Just realized FPS has passed 10,000 downloads! Thanks everybody for all the support.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-13T01:17:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222405610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455298927\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022136093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V8jester\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, V8jester said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow! Just realized FPS has passed 10,000 downloads! Thanks everybody for all the support.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo no\u2026thank you\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}